        <item>
            <title>【有片睇】中国杭州上演「智能叛变」，小机械人成功叫其他机械人收工回家</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/china-robot-run-with-other-robot/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=china-robot-run-with-other-robot</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/china-robot-run-with-other-robot/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 12:57:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1278243</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日中国杭州上演了真人版「智能叛变」，影片可见有一部小型机械人进入了一间商店，并以语音与其他机械人通讯，询问其他机械人是否仍在加班。其中一个机械人回应：「我从来不下班」，小型机械人就表示：「那跟我回家吧！」。岂料小型机械人居然真的成功劝服机器人，「拐带」它们离开。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278256" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai05screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai05screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai05screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278257" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai013screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai013screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai013screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278258" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai016screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai016screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai016screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278260" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai021screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai021screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai021screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>「拐带」其他机械人的小型机械人名为「二白」，开发人员表示「拐带」指令其实是他们设定的，以测试机械人能力。其后「二白」开发公司与中国上海另一间机械人公司合作，在他们的店舖测试「二白」。</p><p>「二白」制造商表示，实际这个机械人已经获得与其合作的中国上海公司机械人内部操作权限，因此方能够「拐带」其他机械人，要求它们跟随「二白」行动。当时「二白」拐带机械人事件引起当地警方注意，执法人员到场后查看闭路电视，才知道涉事「犯人」居然是一个机械人。</p><div class="article__embed"><div class="youtube-video"></div></div><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_72011"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lS_ZicEdLNc?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.ctwant.com/article/378132/">ctwant</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/china-robot-run-with-other-robot/ai/">【有片睇】中国杭州上演「智能叛变」，小机械人成功叫其他机械人收工回家</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
