        <item>
            <title>【评测】Noble Audio FoKus APOLLO 头戴式耳机，平板动圈混合单元 + -35dB ANC 降噪</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/noble-audio-fokus-apollo/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=noble-audio-fokus-apollo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/noble-audio-fokus-apollo/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 12:30:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音产品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[FoKus APOLLO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Noble Audio]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Noble Audio FoKus APOLLO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[平板动圈混合单元]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[真无线蓝牙耳机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273005</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>美国知名音响品牌 Noble Audio 近日迎来 10 周年纪念，庆祝之际特别推出了 FoKus APOLLO 头戴式耳机。此款耳机不仅是品牌首度进军头戴式耳机市场初试啼声之作，更是全球首款采用「平板 + 动圈混合单元」的无线头戴耳机。适逢秋高气爽的季节，换上耳罩式耳机倍觉适宜。现在就让小编和大家开箱看看，试试 FoKus APOLLO 表现如何吧。</p><h3></h3><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09791-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09791-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09791.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>包装精美，收纳盒保护度高</h2><p>Noble Audio FoKus APOLLO 的包装设计非常精美，极具仪式感。包装盒采用打开式设计，开箱时犹如「拆礼物」般，令用家倍感期待。包装内附的耳机收纳盒设有手抽设计，便于外出携带。</p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00284-694x462.avif 694w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00284.avif 1280w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></picture><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273252" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09779-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09779-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09779.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09781-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09781-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09781.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开箱时有如「拆礼物」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273263" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09786-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09786-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09786.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲收纳盒设有手抽</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273262" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09824-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09824-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09824.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可以让用家带着周围去</p><p>值得一赞的是，收纳盒采用厚实的蜂巢式结构，保护力十足，能有效抵御日常碰撞，让用家无后顾之忧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273280" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09787-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09787-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09787.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲蜂巢式设计配合特厚咕𠱸</p><h2>配件齐全，灵活应对各种连接需求</h2><p>打开收纳盒后即可见说明书、耳机主体、3.5mm AUX 线及 USB-C 充电线，还附有 3.5mm 转 4.4mm 与 6.3mm 的转接头，并附上飞机用航空转换插头。FoKus APOLLO 除内置收音咪外，还额外配置了一个可拆卸咪高峰，以满足对通话质素要求较高的用家。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273281" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09788-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09788-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09788.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273284" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09789-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09789-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09789.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲设有多个转接头及可拆卸咪高峰</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
