        <item>
            <title>华为 Mate 70 麒麟 9020 处理器跑分出炉，效能表现达 4nm 制程水平 + 分数与 iPhone 11 Pro 相若</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/huawei-mate-70-kirin-9020/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-mate-70-kirin-9020</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/huawei-mate-70-kirin-9020/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 12:00:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Kirin 9020]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[中国晶片]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[华为]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[麒麟]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[麒麟 9020]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1278137</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日前华为（Huawei）发布最新 Mate 70 系列智能手机（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/27/huawei-mate-70-series/mobile-phone/">相关报道</a>），官方提供了有关 Mate 70 系列的 3 个关键数据，表示与上一代华为 Mate 60 Pro+ 比较，操作流畅度提升 39%，游戏帧率提升 31%，整机效能提升 40%。有网友发现，Mate 70 Pro/Pro+/RS 使用的 Kirin 9020 晶片是全新 8 核心 12 线程晶片。中国科技媒体「数码闲聊站」在微博透露指，这款晶片是业界首款对应 3GPP R18 的 5G-A （即 5.5G）晶片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278166" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129153636-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129153636-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129153636.jpg 927w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/u/6048569942?jumpfrom=weibocom">数码闲聊站@微博</a></p><p>据中国媒体《快科技》报道， Mate 70 使用的晶片为 Kirin 9010，与 Pura 70 系列相同；Mate 70Pro、Pro+ 及 RS 则是采用全新 Kirin 9020 处理器，全部均是 8 核心 12 线程，软件识别则是 12 核心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278153" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fa5f990a28af456e96e5-455x580.jpg" alt="" width="455" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fa5f990a28af456e96e5-455x580.jpg 455w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fa5f990a28af456e96e5.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 455px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/1016/1016305.htm">快科技</a></p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 168px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 19.4947%; height: 24px;"><strong>晶片</strong></td><td style="width: 47.1719%; text-align: center; height: 24px;"><strong>规格</strong></td><td style="width: 16.6667%; text-align: center; height: 24px;"><strong>GPU</strong></td><td style="width: 16.6667%; text-align: center; height: 24px;"><strong>频率</strong></td></tr><tr style="height: 48px;"><td style="width: 19.4947%; height: 48px;">Kirin 9020</td><td style="width: 47.1719%; text-align: center; height: 48px;">2×2.50 GHz+6×2.15 GHz+4×1.6GHz</td><td style="width: 16.6667%; text-align: center; height: 48px;">马良 920</td><td style="width: 16.6667%; text-align: center; height: 48px;">840MHz</td></tr><tr style="height: 48px;"><td style="width: 19.4947%; height: 48px;">Kirin 9010</td><td style="width: 47.1719%; text-align: center; height: 48px;">2×2.30 GHz+6×2.18 GHz+4×1.55GHz</td><td style="width: 16.6667%; text-align: center; height: 48px;">马良 910</td><td style="width: 16.6667%; text-align: center; height: 48px;">750MHz</td></tr><tr style="height: 48px;"><td style="width: 19.4947%; height: 48px;">Kirin 9000S</td><td style="width: 47.1719%; text-align: center; height: 48px;">2×2.62 GHz+6×2.15 GHz+4×1.53 GHz</td><td style="width: 16.6667%; text-align: center; height: 48px;">马良 910</td><td style="width: 16.6667%; text-align: center; height: 48px;">750MHz</td></tr></tbody></table><p>Geekbench 数据显示，Kirin 9020 单核跑分结果为 1595 分，多核跑分结果为 4984 分，单核表现与 2019 年推出的 iPhone 11 Pro 采用的 A13 晶片相若。A13 单核跑分结果为 1751 分，多核跑分结果为 4085 分。与 2020 年推出的 iPhone 12 Pro 采用的 A14 晶片相比，表现就略逊一筹。A14 单核跑分结果为 2178 分，多核跑分结果为 5457 分</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155449-475x580.png" alt="" width="475" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155449-475x580.png 475w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155449.png 737w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 475px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155053-469x580.png" alt="" width="469" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155053-469x580.png 469w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155053.png 727w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 469px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple A13 跑分结果，图片来源：<a href="https://browser.geekbench.com/v6/cpu/9128142">Geekbench</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278175" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155358-466x580.png" alt="" width="466" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155358-466x580.png 466w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155358.png 723w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 466px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple A14 跑分结果，图片来源：<a href="https://browser.geekbench.com/v6/cpu/9128142">Geekbench</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=38rblx74Hn4&amp;ab_channel=SemanticTech">Semantic Tech@YouTube</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/1016/1016305.htm">My Drivers</a>、<a href="https://browser.geekbench.com/v6/cpu/9128142">Geekbench</a>、<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/u/6048569942?jumpfrom=weibocom">数码闲聊站@微博</a></p><br /><b>
